{
  "texts": [
    "Each question was evaluated by two blinded physicians.",
    "If there was disagreement in the grade assigned, a third evaluator determined the final grade.",
    "Any response that was felt to be equally correct and specific, as compared to the provided answer, was marked as correct.",
    "Physicians used UpToDate 23, MKSAPP 24, and StatPearls 25 to verify accuracy of answers when needed.",
    "For this evaluation we used the OpenAI Davinci-003 model via an OpenAI API to provide GPT-3.5 responses and GPT-4 model via an OpenAI API to provide GPT-4 responses."
  ]
}